<dl class="field-list simple">
<dt class="field-odd">Parameters</dt>
<dd class="field-odd"><p><strong>payload</strong> (<a class="reference internal" href="#discord.RawBulkMessageDeleteEvent" title="discord.RawBulkMessageDeleteEvent"><code class="xref py py-class docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">RawBulkMessageDeleteEvent</span></code></a>) – The raw event payload data.</p>
</dd>
</dl>
