<p>This is equivalent to calling <a class="reference internal" href="#discord.ClientUser.avatar_url_as" title="discord.ClientUser.avatar_url_as"><code class="xref py py-meth docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">avatar_url_as()</span></code></a> with
the default parameters (i.e. webp/gif detection and a size of 1024).</p>
