<p>Retrieves the content of this attachment as a <a class="reference external" href="https://docs.python.org/3/library/stdtypes.html#bytes" title="(in Python v3.9)"><code class="xref py py-class docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">bytes</span></code></a> object.</p>
