<li><p><strong>vanity_code</strong> (<a class="reference external" href="https://docs.python.org/3/library/stdtypes.html#str" title="(in Python v3.9)"><code class="xref py py-class docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">str</span></code></a>) – The new vanity code for the guild.</p></li>
