<li><p><strong>reason</strong> (Optional[<a class="reference external" href="https://docs.python.org/3/library/stdtypes.html#str" title="(in Python v3.9)"><code class="xref py py-class docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">str</span></code></a>]) – The reason for cloning this channel. Shows up on the audit log.</p></li>
