<dl class="py method">
<dt id="discord.DMChannel.permissions_for">
<code class="sig-name descname">permissions_for</code><span class="sig-paren">(</span><em class="sig-param"><span class="n">user</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="default_value">None</span></em><span class="sig-paren">)</span><a class="headerlink" href="#discord.DMChannel.permissions_for" title="Permalink to this definition">¶</a></dt>
<dd><p>Handles permission resolution for a <a class="reference internal" href="#discord.User" title="discord.User"><code class="xref py py-class docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">User</span></code></a>.</p>
<p>This function is there for compatibility with other channel types.</p>
<p>Actual direct messages do not really have the concept of permissions.</p>
<p>This returns all the Text related permissions set to <code class="docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">True</span></code> except:</p>
<ul class="simple">
<li><p><a class="reference internal" href="#discord.Permissions.send_tts_messages" title="discord.Permissions.send_tts_messages"><code class="xref py py-attr docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">send_tts_messages</span></code></a>: You cannot send TTS messages in a DM.</p></li>
<li><p><a class="reference internal" href="#discord.Permissions.manage_messages" title="discord.Permissions.manage_messages"><code class="xref py py-attr docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">manage_messages</span></code></a>: You cannot delete others messages in a DM.</p></li>
</ul>
<dl class="field-list simple">
<dt class="field-odd">Parameters</dt>
<dd class="field-odd"><p><strong>user</strong> (<a class="reference internal" href="#discord.User" title="discord.User"><code class="xref py py-class docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">User</span></code></a>) – The user to check permissions for. This parameter is ignored
but kept for compatibility.</p>
</dd>
<dt class="field-even">Returns</dt>
<dd class="field-even"><p>The resolved permissions.</p>
</dd>
<dt class="field-odd">Return type</dt>
<dd class="field-odd"><p><a class="reference internal" href="#discord.Permissions" title="discord.Permissions"><code class="xref py py-class docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">Permissions</span></code></a></p>
</dd>
</dl>
</dd></dl>

